{"tid":1383812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"完啦，好嗎？分化完未？説好的兄弟爬山各自努力","createTime":"2019-07-29T18:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T19:52:28.000Z","uid":231480,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2cb9502699f9b5727223335e0b287fe1a2af1e8e","tid":1383812,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:49:04.000Z","msg":"點解呢一兩日出現咁撚多分化勇武和理非post<br />\n<br />\n一時屌人散水，屌劉細良<br />\n另一邊箱屌人勇武送頭，霸道，唔聽意見<br />\n<br />\n好好屌咩！你哋文盲定弱智？今天天琦封信講乜<br />\n<br />\n勇武嘅繼續勇武，呢幾日諗定好戰術，練好身體，買齊裝<br />\n（唔好同我講自己齊裝，28號嗰晚肯定少咗物資）<br />\n和理非嘅繼續做好文宣，叫人罷工，Keep住道火，外國呈請又好，課金又好，跟進被補義士，受傷義士又好⋯⋯<br />\n咁多嘢做你咁得閒上連登互屌<br />\n<br />\nAny肥,長篇大論唔講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n利申：和理非同勇武做過，到而家都係"},{"pid":"5d1127898378004e20a8459b660a810fe57767a5","tid":1383812,"uid":231480,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:50:56.000Z","msg":"7月30日正午12點，所以分化Post自動收皮"},{"pid":"28f1cfa1a50152d9c75ba91b4451eecc0d673342","tid":1383812,"uid":231480,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5d1127898378004e20a8459b660a810fe57767a5","tid":1383812,"uid":231480,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:50:56.000Z","msg":"7月30日正午12點，所以分化Post自動收皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:51:13.000Z","msg":"7月30日正午12點，所以分化Post自動收皮"},{"pid":"c6360ba9b4e8b19bf15202669e07a12290241c65","tid":1383812,"uid":213781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:51:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"284faa8a740d181f20f21b35d7d4d83219c05d4d","tid":1383812,"uid":263905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:52:28.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7K6NYkk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7K6NYkk.png&h=d5e0d3a1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/soO1ikk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.c